                <li>Five tools bundled for one price (KWFinder, SERPChecker, etc.)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Daily limits hit fast on the Basic tier</li>
                <li>Backlink data is shallower than Ahrefs</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Beginners who want a clean research toolkit at low price.</div>
            <a href="https://mangools.com/" class="tool-cta-btn" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Visit Mangools →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">05</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">KeySearch</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best cheap keyword research alternative</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$17<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Starter plan</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it does better</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Long-tail keyword discovery for low-competition niches</li>
                <li>Includes YouTube and Amazon keyword tools</li>
                <li>Annual deal cuts price to ~$13/mo</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Backlink data is limited compared to Ahrefs</li>
                <li>UI feels older than Mangools or Ubersuggest</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Affiliate and niche bloggers chasing long-tail topics.</div>
            <a href="https://www.keysearch.co/" class="tool-cta-btn" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Visit KeySearch →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
