              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best free SEO audit tool</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">Free<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">–$50</span></div>
              <div class="per">Premium plan</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it does better</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Strong free-tier on-page and crawl audit</li>
                <li>Visual sitemap explorer for site architecture</li>
                <li>Single-screen prioritised fix list</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Keyword and backlink data lag the leaders</li>
                <li>Free tier caps at 1,000 crawled pages</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Solo developers who want free on-page + crawl audits.</div>
            <a href="https://www.seobility.net/" class="tool-cta-btn" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Visit Seobility →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">07</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">LowFruits</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best affordable low-competition keyword finder</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$29<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Standard plan</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
